Wool Plaid Suit
Long sleeve worsted wool single breasted two button plaid suit
* Notch lapel with buttonhole, nonfunctional button cuffs and back side vents
* Ticket and two flap pockets
* Fully lined with interior pockets

<b>Flat front straight leg wool plaid trousers</b>
* Zippered fly with extended button tab, hidden hook-and-bar and interior button tab closures and belt loops
